a=10
name="Neeraj" (within parenthesis)
age=29
echo "The age of $name is $age"

=====
cmd output as a variable

Hostname=$(hostname)
Pwd=$(pwd)

echo "The hostname of this machine is $Hostname and path is $Pwd"

=====
contant variable that can not be changed 
